channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-21307] Need to set GzipJSONMessageEncoder as default config for EVENT_MESSAGE_FACTORY.
item.description: Currently, we use JsonMessageEncoder as the default message factory for Notification events. As the size of some of the events are really huge and cause OOM issues in RDBMS. So, it is needed to enable GzipJSONMessageEncoder as default message factory to optimise the memory usage.
item.summary: Need to set GzipJSONMessageEncoder as default config for EVENT_MESSAGE_FACTORY.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
